&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;15&quot; data-local-id=&quot;289faca6c867&quot;&gt;We’re seeking a Senior Platform/Real-Time Embedded Firmware Engineer with strong low-level embedded software expertise and a passion for building robust, deterministic firmware for safety-critical control systems. This role focuses on the real-time firmware foundation that enables actuators, motor drives, &lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_kqswh2mm&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_5pioz8co _189e1dm9 _1il9buyh _19lc184f _d0altlke&quot; data-testid=&quot;definition-highlighter&quot;&gt;BMS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, sensors, and vehicle-level systems to operate reliably.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;384&quot; data-local-id=&quot;bac3ba8f59b4&quot;&gt;You will architect, implement, and maintain firmware across real-time microcontroller platforms, owning BSPs, drivers, &lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_kqswh2mm&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_5pioz8co _189e1dm9 _1il9buyh _19lc184f _d0altlke&quot; data-testid=&quot;definition-highlighter&quot;&gt;RTOS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;/bare-metal execution, timing, peripheral interfaces, diagnostics hooks, and hardware bring-up. This role works closely with embedded systems, motor control, &lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;BMS&lt;/span&gt;, and vehicle control software engineers to ensure the platform layer is reliable, reusable, and deterministic.&lt;/p&gt;
