&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;836&quot; data-local-id=&quot;543931aa965a&quot;&gt;Design and maintain real-time firmware architecture for safety-critical embedded control platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;836&quot; data-local-id=&quot;543931aa965a&quot;&gt;Own timing-sensitive firmware layers, interrupt structure, task scheduling, execution order, and deterministic data flow between hardware, drivers, middleware, and application software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1123&quot; data-local-id=&quot;125d8adc5052&quot;&gt;Develop firmware frameworks that support reusable control execution, communication, diagnostics, monitoring, and system integration across multiple projects.&lt;/li&gt;
